IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. STRINGMANIPULATION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-STRING PIC X(100).
01 WS-NEW-STRING PIC X(100).
01 WS-LENGTH PIC 9(3).
01 WS-I PIC 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "Enter a string: ".
    ACCEPT WS-STRING.
    COMPUTE WS-LENGTH = FUNCTION LENGTH(WS-STRING).
    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM WS-LENGTH BY -1 UNTIL WS-I = 0
        STRING WS-STRING(WS-I:1) DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-NEW-STRING
    END-PERFORM.
    DISPLAY "New string: " WS-NEW-STRING.
    STOP RUN.